snippet.title: A Druid's Duel Trailer
snippet.description: A Druid's Duel is a fast-paced turn-based strategy game set in a world of Celtic lore where players can create and destroy the board by harnessing the power of nature. Available now on Steam for Mac, Windows, and Linux. www.druidsduel.com
